data.text:
Equip your Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge smartphone with the eSIM.me Card and start downloading eSIM profiles online!

Check eSIM.me compatibility

Download the free eSIM.me APP from the Playstore to verify eSIM.me compatibily of your very own Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge.

Then simply insert the eSIM.me Card in the SIM card slot of your Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge smartphone and you are ready to start!

Information about the licenses

• SINGLE: Store up to 2 or 5 eSIM profiles and manage them only on a Samsung Galaxy S6 Edge.

• MULTI: Store up to 5, 7 or 10 eSIM profiles and manage them on any Samsung.

• OMNI: Store up to 15 eSIM profiles and manage them on any Android.
